  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/831710/extras/b18905e1d33071b02424bfc6ace43d33.avif?t=1643382112\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br>Electronic Piano is a simple piano keyboard simulator, which helps to start creating music without any special skill or equipment. Awesome and powerful built in synthesizer will let you generate tons of your own unique sounds. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/831710/extras/ba48dadc4f7710a169335bfc59d468be.avif?t=1643382112\" width=600 height=98 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Electronic Piano Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> MIDI keyboards support<br></li><li> 4 octave keyboard<br></li><li> 2 oscillators<br></li><li> 2 filters<br></li><li> 3 types of waveform<br></li><li> Sound recorder<br></li><li> Neat visual design</li></ul><br>Electronic Piano is a powerful synthesizer for every electronic music lover. Download and have fun!",
